subproject.description:
Following are key outputs of the project:
1. Raising border management awareness and supporting strategic border management capacity; 
2. Strengthening operational techniques and procedures;
3. Training and pilot programmes development; 
4. Establishment of pilot border crossing points and procurement of equipments and IT systems.

